  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Teaching Children Human Rights in Liberia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">What good are your rights if you don&apos;t know you have them? Our program to teach civics, rights awareness and conflict resolution in selected schools and communities is already funded, but we need help printing copies of the Constitution for the students. Liberia is a country still recovering from more than a decade of civil wars and EBOLA outbreak. Help us give citizens the tools to rebuild their own democracy by bringing civics and rights education to every school in Liberia by fall 2016.</narrative>
  </description>
